    "link": "https://ryanrcampbell.com/podcast/writescast-015-keeping-the-science-in-science-fiction-and-the-fiction-too-with-scott-birrenkott/",
    "pubDate": "Fri, 18 Aug 2017 11:00:22 +0000",
