        "__cdata": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I know it says \"Just Me\" in the title, but let's make this show more of a \"Just We,\" shall we? Share with me what it is you're excited about, what has you worried, what you're tussling with; I'd love to feature it on the show. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether in the comments, on social media, or by email at justmewithrr [at] gmail [dot] com, it'd be great to hear from you. Talk to me! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Topics discussed include:</strong> D&amp;D (again), updates on querying, new manuscripts, invitations to join in for future episodes</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->"
