        "__cdata": "[caption id=\"attachment_4738\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"204\"]<img class=\" wp-image-4738\" src=\"https://ryanrcampbell.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/noelleNichols_photo-300x297.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"204\" height=\"202\"> Noelle Nichols[/caption]\n\nWhether you've just completed NaNoWriMo, have otherwise recently finished a manuscript, or finally have a writing habit started, this conversation with Noelle Nichols will surely help you press on with what comes next. Throughout this episode, we discuss how to keep up your momentum and tackle early edits once we've finally completed a manuscript draft.\n\nNoelle is a fantasy author who writes for the sake of finding light in the world. As an avid dreamer, she loves pitting her characters against moral choices, and enjoys exploring the silver lining between good and evil. Her first book,&nbsp;<em>Shadow's Design</em>, is set to debut in the spring of 2018.\n\nYou can find Noelle in the #amwriting community on Twitter (@noelle_nichols), or on her website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://noellenichols.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://noellenichols.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1511892250593000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGzHYuMM4tDa1A05MGq6n7fFY282A\">noellenichols.com</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://ryanrcampbell.com/podcast-download/4736/writescast025.mp3?ref=new_window\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click here to listen to this episode.</a>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>For more episodes of&nbsp;</em>the r. r. campbell writescast<em>, be sure to visit the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ryanrcampbell.com/podcasts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://ryanrcampbell.com/podcasts/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1495054734206000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFb_kjhM3wcafY3cURUgBWjseB4iQ\">podcasts</a>&nbsp;page.</em></p>\n\n\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4411\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/rrcampbellwrites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/featured-image-on-essay-page.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/rrcampbellwrites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/featured-image-on-essay-page.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/rrcampbellwrites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/featured-image-on-essay-page.png?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" data-attachment-id=\"4411\" data-permalink=\"https://ryanrcampbell.com/podcast/writescast020/featured-image-on-essay-page/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/rrcampbellwrites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/featured-image-on-essay-page.png?fit=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1024,512\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"featured image on essay page\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/rrcampbellwrites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/featured-image-on-essay-page.png?fit=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/rrcampbellwrites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/featured-image-on-essay-page.png?fit=825%2C413&amp;ssl=1\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">From now until December 10th, 2017, you can enter to win a FREE manuscript assessment or first fifty-page critique from the show’s host, r. r. campbell!&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.rrcampbellwrites.com/feedback\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click here</a>&nbsp;to learn more!</p>"
