        "__cdata": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Well, writerfolk, this is a wild one. After going #FullMingo in the episode introduction, r.r. campbell and Maggie Derrick explore the challenge that is synopsis writing. As they discuss and debate, they borrow a few bits from the McElroy brothers and take potshots at their capitalist overlords.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://www.publishingcrawl.com/2012/04/17/how-to-write-a-1-page-synopsis/\" target=\"_blank\">Here's the synopsis guide they reference during the episode.</a> And <a href=\"https://ryanrcampbell.com/writingpromptgenerator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">this is the writing prompt generator</a> referenced later on.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks to this episode's sponsors <a href=\"http://www.dandelionwebmarketing.com/\">Dandelion Web Marketing</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://lostlakepress.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Lost Lake Press</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.chicagowrites.org/\" target=\"_blank\">the Chicago Writers Association</a>, and <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://www.kydcandleco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Kill Your Darlings Candle Company</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->"
