        "__cdata": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sometimes a book launch doesn't go as planned, but there's no need to fret. Author Dan Woll is actively relaunching <em>Death on Cache Lake</em>, and he joins us to talk through the challenges and opportunities one might encounter during when <em>re</em>launching one's book.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Want your question or comment featured on a future episode of this show? Say hello at <a href=\"http://www.writescast.net/hello\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">writescast.net/hello</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks to this episode's sponsors <a href=\"http://www.dandelionwebmarketing.com/\">Dandelion Web Marketing</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://lostlakepress.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Lost Lake Press</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.chicagowrites.org/\" target=\"_blank\">the Chicago Writers Association</a>, and <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://www.kydcandleco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Kill Your Darlings Candle Company</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->"
